==Preferences== <!--T:13-->

<!--T:14-->
See also: [[Preferences_Editor|Preferences Editor]] and [[Draft_Preferences|Draft Preferences]].

<!--T:15-->
* The Draft annotation scale widget is optional: {{MenuCommand|Edit → Preferences → Draft → Interface → Show the Draft Scale Widget in the Draft Workbench}}.
* To change the annotation scale without the widget: change the {{MenuCommand|Scale multiplier}} on the {{MenuCommand|Annotation}} tab of the [[Draft_SetStyle|Draft SetStyle]] command. For a scale of {{Value|1:50}} enter {{Value|0.02}}.

